                    .col.xs12.md9
                        div(class="row")
                            h6 Match the meaning with the word.
                        div(class="row mt30" data-ejercicio="unir")
                            div(id="sourceElements" class="ancho250 js-columnas")
                                span(id="Item0_0" class="treeItem" js-bien = 'jsbien' jsvalida = 'jsvalida' onclick="setSource(this)" seleccion valor="1") A get-together
                                span(id="Item0_1" class="treeItem" js-bien = 'jsbien' jsvalida = 'jsvalida' onclick="setSource(this)" seleccion valor="2") A dinner engagement
                                span(id="Item0_2" class="treeItem" js-bien = 'jsbien' jsvalida = 'jsvalida' onclick="setSource(this)" seleccion valor="3") An interview
                                span(id="Item0_3" class="treeItem" js-bien = 'jsbien' jsvalida = 'jsvalida' onclick="setSource(this)" seleccion valor="4") An appointment
                                span(id="Item0_4" class="treeItem" js-bien = 'jsbien' jsvalida = 'jsvalida' onclick="setSource(this)" seleccion valor="5") A check-up
                                span(id="Item0_5" class="treeItem" js-bien = 'jsbien' jsvalida = 'jsvalida' onclick="setSource(this)" seleccion valor="6") A date
                            div(id="linecanvas" style="width: 60px;")
                            div(id="targetElements" class="ancho350 js-columnas")
                                span(id="Item1_0" class="treeItem" jsblock = 'jsblock' jsvalidb = 'jsvalidb' onclick="setTarget(this)" seleccion valor="4") A formal arrangement to meet or visit someone at a fixed time and place.
                                span(id="Item1_1" class="treeItem" jsblock = 'jsblock' jsvalidb = 'jsvalidb' onclick="setTarget(this)" seleccion valor="1") An informal meeting or social gathering
                                span(id="Item1_2" class="treeItem" jsblock = 'jsblock' jsvalidb = 'jsvalidb' onclick="setTarget(this)" seleccion valor="5") A medical examination to test the general state of your health.
                                span(id="Item1_3" class="treeItem" jsblock = 'jsblock' jsvalidb = 'jsvalidb' onclick="setTarget(this)" seleccion valor="6") A planned romantic meeting between two people.
                                span(id="Item1_4" class="treeItem" jsblock = 'jsblock' jsvalidb = 'jsvalidb' onclick="setTarget(this)" seleccion valor="2") An arrangement to meet somebody for an evening meal (very formal).
                                span(id="Item1_5" class="treeItem" jsblock = 'jsblock' jsvalidb = 'jsvalidb' onclick="setTarget(this)" seleccion valor="3") A meeting in which someone asks you questions to see if you are suitable for a job or course.
